Supreme Court of India
Tax Recovery Officer, Vijayawada vs Karri Ramakrishna Reddy on 10 November, 1983Equivalent citations: 1984 145 ITR 739 SC, 1984 Supp (1) SCC 596
Author: V Tulzapurkar
Bench: R Pathak, S Mukharji, V Tulzapurkar
ORDER
  

V.D. Tulzapurkar, J.


1. Heard Counsel.


2. In all the facts and circumstances of the case and having regard to the smallness of the amount involved, we do not think that this Court should interfere with the impugned order of the High Court. The appeal is, therefore, dismissed.
  


